(13, 1, NULL, NULL, 'SEO Specialist', 'seo-specialist', '<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"264\" data-end=\"286\"><strong data-start=\"268\" data-end=\"284\">Job Summary:</strong></h3>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"287\" data-end=\"585\">We seek a results-driven <strong data-start=\"323\" data-end=\"341\">SEO Specialist</strong> to optimize our website content, improve search engine rankings, and increase organic traffic. The ideal candidate is knowledgeable about current SEO trends, proficient in analytics tools, and has experience with both on-page and off-page SEO.</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"592\" data-end=\"621\"><strong data-start=\"596\" data-end=\"621\">Key Responsibilities:</strong></h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"623\" data-end=\"1316\">\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"623\" data-end=\"736\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"625\" data-end=\"736\">Conduct comprehensive <strong data-start=\"647\" data-end=\"667\">keyword research</strong> and implement SEO strategies to increase rankings on search engines.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"737\" data-end=\"798\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"739\" data-end=\"798\">Optimize website content, landing pages, and blogs for SEO.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"799\" data-end=\"927\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"801\" data-end=\"927\">Monitor and analyze website performance using tools like <strong data-start=\"858\" data-end=\"878\">Google Analytics</strong>, <strong data-start=\"880\" data-end=\"898\">Search Console</strong>, <strong data-start=\"900\" data-end=\"910\">Ahrefs</strong>, or <strong data-start=\"915\" data-end=\"926\">SEMRush</strong>.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"928\" data-end=\"1001\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"930\" data-end=\"1001\">Perform regular <strong data-start=\"946\" data-end=\"970\">technical SEO audits</strong> and implement necessary fixes.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1002\" data-end=\"1075\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1004\" data-end=\"1075\">Build and maintain <strong data-start=\"1023\" data-end=\"1046\">backlink strategies</strong> to improve domain authority.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1076\" data-end=\"1163\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1078\" data-end=\"1163\">Collaborate with content creators and web developers to implement SEO best practices.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1164\" data-end=\"1240\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1166\" data-end=\"1240\">Stay updated with <strong data-start=\"1184\" data-end=\"1219\">search engine algorithm changes</strong> and industry trends.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1241\" data-end=\"1316\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1243\" data-end=\"1316\">Generate performance reports and present recommendations for improvement.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1323\" data-end=\"1355\"><strong data-start=\"1327\" data-end=\"1355\">Qualifications &amp; Skills:</strong></h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1357\" data-end=\"1940\">\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1357\" data-end=\"1459\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1359\" data-end=\"1459\">Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Marketing, Communications, IT, or a related field (preferred but not required).</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1460\" data-end=\"1513\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1462\" data-end=\"1513\">Minimum of [2&ndash;3] years of proven experience in SEO.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1514\" data-end=\"1606\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1516\" data-end=\"1606\">Strong understanding of search engine algorithms, ranking methods, and current SEO trends.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1607\" data-end=\"1711\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1609\" data-end=\"1711\">Hands-on experience with <strong data-start=\"1634\" data-end=\"1647\">SEO tools</strong> (e.g., Google Analytics, SEMrush, Moz, Ahrefs, Screaming Frog).</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1712\" data-end=\"1796\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1714\" data-end=\"1796\">Basic knowledge of <strong data-start=\"1733\" data-end=\"1747\">HTML, CSS,</strong> and website platforms like WordPress or Shopify.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1797\" data-end=\"1863\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1799\" data-end=\"1863\">Excellent analytical, problem-solving, and communication skills.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1864\" data-end=\"1940\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1866\" data-end=\"1940\">Ability to work independently and manage multiple projects simultaneously.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr class=\"\" data-start=\"1942\" data-end=\"1945\">\r\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1947\" data-end=\"1989\"><strong data-start=\"1951\" data-end=\"1989\">Preferred Certifications (a plus):</strong></h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1990\" data-end=\"2122\">\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1990\" data-end=\"2024\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1992\" data-end=\"2024\">Google Analytics Certification</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2025\" data-end=\"2068\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2027\" data-end=\"2068\">HubSpot Content Marketing Certification</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2069\" data-end=\"2091\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2071\" data-end=\"2091\">Yoast SEO Training</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2092\" data-end=\"2122\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2094\" data-end=\"2122\">SEMrush SEO Toolkit Course</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr class=\"\" data-start=\"2124\" data-end=\"2127\">\r\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"2129\" data-end=\"2151\"><strong data-start=\"2133\" data-end=\"2151\">What We Offer:</strong></h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"2152\" data-end=\"2315\">\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2152\" data-end=\"2174\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2154\" data-end=\"2174\">Competitive salary</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2175\" data-end=\"2212\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2177\" data-end=\"2212\">Growth and learning opportunities</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2213\" data-end=\"2247\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2215\" data-end=\"2247\">Collaborative team environment</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"287\" data-end=\"585\">&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Competitive', 2, 'full-time', 'Nairobi, Kenya', 106, NULL, '2025-05-08 05:26:55', '2025-05-21 09:43:49', 'closed', NULL, 1),
(14, 1, NULL, NULL, 'Business Developer – Tendering Specialist', 'business-developer-tendering-specialist', '<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"289\" data-end=\"310\"><strong data-start=\"293\" data-end=\"308\">Job Summary</strong></h3>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"311\" data-end=\"667\">We are seeking an experienced and proactive <strong data-start=\"355\" data-end=\"377\">Business Developer</strong> with a strong background in <strong data-start=\"406\" data-end=\"438\">tendering and bid management</strong>. The successful candidate will be responsible for identifying new business opportunities, managing the end-to-end tendering process, and building strong relationships with key clients and stakeholders to support business growth.</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"669\" data-end=\"697\"><strong data-start=\"673\" data-end=\"697\">Key Responsibilities</strong></h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"1463\">\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"779\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"700\" data-end=\"779\">Identify and pursue new business opportunities in line with company objectives.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"780\" data-end=\"866\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"782\" data-end=\"866\">Monitor tender portals and relevant platforms for potential tenders, RFQs, and RFPs.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"867\" data-end=\"972\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"869\" data-end=\"972\">Prepare, review, and submit high-quality proposals and tender documentation within specified deadlines.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"973\" data-end=\"1100\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"975\" data-end=\"1100\">Coordinate with internal departments (technical, finance, legal, etc.) to gather required information for tender submissions.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1101\" data-end=\"1168\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1103\" data-end=\"1168\">Ensure compliance with tender requirements and improve win rates.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1169\" data-end=\"1225\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1171\" data-end=\"1225\">Maintain accurate records of all bids and submissions.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1226\" data-end=\"1323\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1228\" data-end=\"1323\">Develop strong relationships with existing and prospective clients, partners, and stakeholders.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1324\" data-end=\"1395\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1326\" data-end=\"1395\">Conduct market and competitor analysis to inform strategic decisions.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1396\" data-end=\"1463\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1398\" data-end=\"1463\">Support contract negotiation and post-award activities as needed.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1465\" data-end=\"1485\"><strong data-start=\"1469\" data-end=\"1485\">Requirements</strong></h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1486\" data-end=\"1987\">\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1486\" data-end=\"1573\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1488\" data-end=\"1573\">Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Business Administration, Procurement, Sales, or a related field.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1574\" data-end=\"1650\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1576\" data-end=\"1650\">Minimum of <strong data-start=\"1587\" data-end=\"1600\">3&ndash;5 years</strong> of experience in business development and tendering.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1651\" data-end=\"1723\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1653\" data-end=\"1723\">Proven track record of successful bid submissions and business growth.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1724\" data-end=\"1798\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1726\" data-end=\"1798\">Strong knowledge of government and private sector procurement processes.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1799\" data-end=\"1858\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1801\" data-end=\"1858\">Excellent writing, communication, and negotiation skills.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1859\" data-end=\"1916\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1861\" data-end=\"1916\">Highly organized, detail-oriented, and deadline-driven.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1917\" data-end=\"1987\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1919\" data-end=\"1987\">Proficiency in Microsoft Office and tender management systems/tools.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1989\" data-end=\"2013\"><strong data-start=\"1993\" data-end=\"2013\">Preferred Skills</strong></h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"2014\" data-end=\"2219\">\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2014\" data-end=\"2096\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2016\" data-end=\"2096\">Experience in (industry) construction, IT, logistics.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2097\" data-end=\"2168\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2099\" data-end=\"2168\">Ability to work independently and as part of a cross-functional team.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2169\" data-end=\"2219\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2171\" data-end=\"2219\">Strong analytical and strategic thinking skills.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, 'Competitive', 2, 'full-time', 'Nairobi, Kenya', 106, NULL, '2025-05-08 05:33:09', '2025-05-21 09:42:57', 'closed', NULL, 1),
(15, 1, NULL, NULL, 'Data Analyst', 'data-analyst', '<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"310\" data-end=\"332\"><strong data-start=\"314\" data-end=\"330\">Job Summary:</strong></h3>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"333\" data-end=\"697\">We are seeking a detail-oriented and analytical Data Analyst to join our team. The ideal candidate will be responsible for collecting, processing, and analyzing data to help drive strategic decision-making and improve business outcomes. This role requires strong analytical skills, a passion for data, and the ability to translate numbers into actionable insights.</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"699\" data-end=\"728\"><strong data-start=\"703\" data-end=\"728\">Key Responsibilities:</strong></h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"729\" data-end=\"1305\">\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"729\" data-end=\"795\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"731\" data-end=\"795\">Collect, clean, and analyze large datasets from various sources.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"796\" data-end=\"904\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"798\" data-end=\"904\">Develop and maintain dashboards, reports, and visualizations using tools like Power BI, Tableau, or Excel.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"905\" data-end=\"995\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"907\" data-end=\"995\">Interpret data trends and patterns to identify insights and support business strategies.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"996\" data-end=\"1085\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"998\" data-end=\"1085\">Collaborate with cross-functional teams to understand data needs and deliver solutions.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1086\" data-end=\"1167\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1088\" data-end=\"1167\">Ensure data integrity and perform quality checks on incoming and existing data.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1168\" data-end=\"1236\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1170\" data-end=\"1236\">Assist in developing predictive models and forecasting techniques.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1237\" data-end=\"1305\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1239\" data-end=\"1305\">Prepare clear and concise reports for management and stakeholders.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1307\" data-end=\"1330\"><strong data-start=\"1311\" data-end=\"1330\">Qualifications:</strong></h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1331\" data-end=\"1832\">\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1331\" data-end=\"1441\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1333\" data-end=\"1441\">Bachelor\'s degree in Data Science, Statistics, Mathematics, Computer Science, Economics, or a related field.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1442\" data-end=\"1512\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1444\" data-end=\"1512\">Proven experience as a Data Analyst or in a similar analytical role.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1513\" data-end=\"1609\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1515\" data-end=\"1609\">Proficiency in SQL, Excel, and at least one data visualization tool (e.g., Power BI, Tableau).</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1610\" data-end=\"1689\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1612\" data-end=\"1689\">Knowledge of statistical programming languages such as R or Python is a plus.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1690\" data-end=\"1746\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1692\" data-end=\"1746\">Strong problem-solving skills and attention to detail.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1747\" data-end=\"1832\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1749\" data-end=\"1832\">Excellent communication skills and ability to explain complex data in simple terms.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1834\" data-end=\"1859\"><strong data-start=\"1838\" data-end=\"1859\">Preferred Skills:</strong></h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1860\" data-end=\"2050\">\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1860\" data-end=\"1913\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1862\" data-end=\"1913\">Experience with data warehousing and ETL processes.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1914\" data-end=\"1973\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1916\" data-end=\"1973\">Familiarity with cloud platforms (e.g., AWS, Azure, GCP).</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1974\" data-end=\"2050\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1976\" data-end=\"2050\">Ability to work independently and manage multiple projects simultaneously.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"2052\" data-end=\"2074\"><strong data-start=\"2056\" data-end=\"2074\">What We Offer:</strong></h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"2075\" data-end=\"2222\">\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2075\" data-end=\"2116\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2077\" data-end=\"2116\">Competitive salary and benefits package</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2117\" data-end=\"2172\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2119\" data-end=\"2172\">Opportunities for professional growth and development</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2173\" data-end=\"2222\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2175\" data-end=\"2222\">A collaborative and innovative work environment</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, 'Competitive', 1, 'full-time', 'Nairobi, Kenya', 106, NULL, '2025-05-08 05:37:50', '2025-05-21 09:43:30', 'closed', NULL, 1),
(16, 1, NULL, NULL, 'Sales and Marketing Associate – Agricultural Inputs & Irrigation Solutions', 'sales-and-marketing-associate-agricultural-inputs-irrigation-solutions', '<p class=\"\" data-start=\"327\" data-end=\"747\"><strong data-start=\"327\" data-end=\"344\">Job Overview:</strong><br data-start=\"344\" data-end=\"347\">We are seeking a motivated and results-driven Sales and Marketing Associate to join our team. The ideal candidate will be responsible for promoting and selling agricultural inputs and irrigation machinery, including greenhouse films, dam liners, PP pipes, PVC fittings, and seedling trays. This is a great opportunity to work in a dynamic and fast-paced environment with room for professional growth.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"749\" data-end=\"774\"><strong data-start=\"749\" data-end=\"774\">Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"775\" data-end=\"1162\">\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"775\" data-end=\"840\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"777\" data-end=\"840\">Develop and implement effective sales and marketing strategies.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"841\" data-end=\"916\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"843\" data-end=\"916\">Promote agricultural and irrigation products to existing and new clients.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"917\" data-end=\"983\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"919\" data-end=\"983\">Conduct market research and identify new business opportunities.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"984\" data-end=\"1056\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"986\" data-end=\"1056\">Maintain strong customer relationships and ensure client satisfaction.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1057\" data-end=\"1162\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1059\" data-end=\"1162\">Prepare reports and presentations using Microsoft Office and design marketing materials with Photoshop.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1164\" data-end=\"1187\"><strong data-start=\"1164\" data-end=\"1187\">Key Qualifications:</strong></p>\r\n<ol data-start=\"1188\" data-end=\"1740\">\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1188\" data-end=\"1257\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1191\" data-end=\"1257\"><strong data-start=\"1191\" data-end=\"1212\">Bachelor&rsquo;s Degree</strong> in Environmental and Biosystems Engineering.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1258\" data-end=\"1372\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1261\" data-end=\"1372\"><strong data-start=\"1261\" data-end=\"1274\">0&ndash;2 years</strong> of experience in sales/marketing of agricultural inputs and irrigation systems (added advantage).</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1373\" data-end=\"1460\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1376\" data-end=\"1460\"><strong data-start=\"1376\" data-end=\"1409\">Proficiency in software tools</strong>: Microsoft Excel, Word, PowerPoint, and Photoshop.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1461\" data-end=\"1605\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1464\" data-end=\"1605\"><strong data-start=\"1464\" data-end=\"1502\">Valid Police Clearance Certificate</strong>, willingness to travel for business/marketing purposes; a valid driving license is an added advantage.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1606\" data-end=\"1740\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1609\" data-end=\"1740\"><strong data-start=\"1609\" data-end=\"1640\">Strong interpersonal skills</strong> with a proactive, goal-oriented attitude and the ability to work independently and collaboratively.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1742\" data-end=\"1769\"><strong data-start=\"1742\" data-end=\"1769\">Additional Information:</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1770\" data-end=\"1927\">\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1770\" data-end=\"1825\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1772\" data-end=\"1825\">Competitive salary and performance-based commissions.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1826\" data-end=\"1896\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1828\" data-end=\"1896\">Opportunity to grow your career in a supportive and innovative team.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1897\" data-end=\"1927\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1899\" data-end=\"1927\">Men are encouraged to apply.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, '20,000-25000 USh', 8, 'full-time', 'Kampala Uganda', 106, NULL, '2025-05-08 05:41:43', '2025-05-08 05:44:34', 'open', '2025-05-25', 1),
(17, 1, NULL, NULL, 'Deputy Manager – Operations', 'deputy-manager-operations', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Profile &ndash; Roles and Responsibilities</strong><br><strong>Areas of Responsibility &amp; brief description</strong><br><strong>Responsibility</strong><br>Level<br>1. Manage all day-to-day activities (administrative and functional)<br>Conducted at the Visa Application Centre, which involves:<br><strong>&szlig;</strong> Document scrutiny &amp; verification for visa processing<br><strong>&szlig; </strong>Handling cash &amp; bank-related transactions if assigned<br><strong>&szlig;</strong> Maintaining &amp; recording all application data in a timely and<br>accurate manner<br>&szlig; Ensuring all administration &amp; logistics of passport delivery<br>to consulate/applicant/logistics company, etc.<br>Full<br>2. Conduct regular Audits for all processes &amp; implement all new<br>process rollouts or changes<br>&nbsp;Full<br>3. Identify incorrect or incomplete information by regular quality<br>checks, thereby ensuring the accuracy of the visa application<br>&nbsp;Full<br>4. Ensure regular Error Monitoring - To monitor, track, and reduce the<br>number of errors every month, within acceptable limits<br>Full<br>5. Maintain &amp; improve level of customer &amp; mission satisfaction by<br>enhancing procedures and continuously innovating methods to<br>Increase productivity and cost effectiveness. Ensure that the Teams<br>are aligned &amp; contribute towards the achievement of parameters<br>enlisted in the Team Objective Tracker</p>\r\n<p>6. Maintain adherence to the Service Level Agreements for all<br>processes and ensure adherence to Standard Operating Procedures,<br>manuals, etc., without any deviation. Ensure that the Teams are<br>mentored &amp; worked towards adherence to all SOPs/ processes,<br>required to be complied with, from an Organizational &amp; ISO<br>perspective.<br>Full<br>7. Ensure compliance with VFS Global defined principles, policies &amp;<br>procedures as applicable to the role<br>Full<br>8. Maintain high standards of ethics, integrity, and compliance with<br>corporate procedures<br>Full<br>9. Ensure that the entire process is completed within the mandated<br>Turn Around Time<br>- Ensure that the Teams are aligned &amp; contribute towards<br>achievement of parameters listed in the Team Objective Tracker<br>Full<br>10. Ensure no penalties are incurred and monitor, track, and maintain<br>internal errors<br>- Ensures that the Teams are aligned &amp; contribute towards<br>achievement of parameters listed in the Team Objective Tracker<br>Full<br>11. Ensure personal &amp; professional development for self and team by<br>conducting training regularly (product &amp; process)<br>Ensure that all staff attend the training scheduled by HR &amp; ensure<br>Effective Process Monitoring, by conducting an Internal Process<br>Certifications (OCLs) for all staff.<br>Full<br>12. Assist staff when needed and handle<br>applicant/customer escalations<br>Full<br>13. Liaise with various support functions to handle team-related queries. Full<br>14. Ensure delivery of Value Added Services options and achievement<br>of the VAS targets for the VAC<br>Partial<br>15. Manage VAC productivity and VAC security (Physical &amp; data) Partial<br>16. Mentor the team regularly, thereby ensuring a successor is<br>Created for the position &ndash; to assist the Manager/Unit Manager in<br>Succession planning<br>Partial<br><strong>Indicative KRA&rsquo;s/Budgetary and Revenue Responsibilities</strong><br>1. Productivity: Targets met as prescribed in Team Objective Tracker.<br>2. VAS Target:<br>- Ensures updating of Productivity &amp; VAS Conversion Grid &ndash; to track performance on a<br>weekly/monthly/basis &ndash; data available for H1 &amp; H2 appraisal<br>- Targets to be shared with the staff &amp; progress reviewed at a defined frequency,<br>(recommended weekly), and<br>- Incentives to be disbursed to the staff, as per achievement, on a monthly basis.<br>3. Customer satisfaction (Applicants) Effective Complaint Resolution<br>- Complaint Tracking &ndash;process in place to ensure complaints are monitored, repeats<br>identified, RCA &amp; Action Plan implemented to prevent recurrence<br>- Percentage of Complaints are within prescribed limits (&lt; 0.05% of Application<br>Volumes)<br>- Ensures 100% complaints are responded within 48 hours of receipt.<br>4. Data entry errors - Error Monitoring - To monitor track and reduce the number of errors<br>every month, within acceptable limits<br>5. Late reporting /unauthorized absenteeism &ndash; Team Management<br>6. Attending training programmes&ndash; Adherence to Annual Training Calendar (Trainings<br>scheduled by HR)<br>Ensures all trainings attended by self &amp; team.<br>7. VOC / VOM &ndash; Targets met as prescribed in Team Objective Tracker.<br>D/HR/222_VFS Global Document _ JD _ Operations, Ver. 1.0 Internal Page 32 of 39<br>Partnering Governments. Providing Solutions.<br>8. Adherence to mandated TAT (Turnaround Time) &ndash; TAT Targets met as prescribed in<br>Team Objective Tracker.<br>9. MOR Completed - Reported Timely - MOM Recorded &amp; Closure Completed, for previous<br>open points<br>- Assists Manager in compilation of reports accurately &amp; on time.<br>10. Internal Process Assessments (OCL&rsquo;s) completed - for all direct reportees (for 100%<br>staff twice a month &ndash; 1 announced &amp; 1 unannounced)<br>11. Conformance to ISO Audit Requirements - Internal Calibration (RCA in place -<br>Implementation Evident)<br>12. Timely Completion - Reporting (Weekly/Fortnightly/Monthly/Quarterly, or as per<br>desired frequency)<br>13. Assist reporting manager to complete Financial Audits/ Compliance Certificate to be<br>completed every month, for all Units, and sign-off recorded &amp; sent to Zonal Finance, as<br>applicable.<br>14. Staff Reward &amp; Recognition Culture to be encouraged &ndash; Staff of the month, employee of<br>the Quarter, etc.<br>15. Zero Incidents for any Operations, related to Process Integrity, Loss of Passports, Staff<br>Integrity<br>16. Immediate reporting of Incidents to Immediate Reporting Manager &amp; Head of<br>Operations &ndash; Zone/Country/Region<br>17. Assist reporting manager to compile a Detailed Investigative report, to be shared with<br>all stakeholders, including Immediate Reporting Manager &amp; Head of Operations &ndash;<br>Zone/Country/Region, Security, any other; within 24 hours of the incident.<br>18. Completion of RCA &amp; Action Plan to prevent recurrence of any Incidents, averse to VFS<br>Global&rsquo;s business interests.<br>19. Completion of WB Projects Completion - to ensure that the team works on execution of<br>WB Project, to achieve Continuous Improvement<br><strong>Key Interactions within and outside of VFS Global</strong><br><strong>External Internal</strong><br>1. Travel Agents / Applicants 1. Departments within VFS Global<br>2. Courier service 2. VAS Team<br>3. Vendors &amp; Consultants 3. Regional Operations Team<br>4. IT, HR &amp; other support functions<br><strong>Qualification &amp; Experience</strong> (Education, Experience, specific knowledge, skills,<br>understanding, attitude)<br><strong>Education</strong>: Minimum: Graduate or global equivalent degree<br>&nbsp;Additional: Post&ndash;Graduate or global equivalent<br>Experience: 2 &ndash; 5 years&rsquo; experience, preferably in Travel and Tourism or the Service industry<br>Knowledge &amp; Key Skills:<br>&middot; Proficiency in MS office &amp; good typing speed<br>&middot; Adaptability and presence of mind to handle customer queries<br>and complaints<br>&middot; In-depth knowledge and understanding of systems and<br>processes<br>&middot; Ability to innovate and enhance procedures and methods to<br>increase productivity &amp; cost effectiveness<br>&middot; Team management skills&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'UGX 2,610,340', 1, 'full-time', 'Kampala Uganda', 106, NULL, '2025-05-19 08:50:28', '2025-05-19 08:51:21', 'open', '2025-05-27', 1),
(18, 1, NULL, NULL, 'Compliance & Regulatory Specialist', 'compliance-regulatory-specialist', '<p><strong>Job Overview: </strong></p>\r\n<p>We are seeking a detail-oriented Compliance &amp; Regulatory Specialist to ensure our tech operations adhere to all legal and regulatory requirements. The ideal candidate will play a key role in maintaining trust and transparency as our company grows.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\r\n<p>● Monitor and ensure compliance with relevant financial regulations.</p>\r\n<p>● Liaise with regulatory authorities and internal teams.</p>\r\n<p>● Develop and implement compliance policies and procedures.</p>\r\n<p>● Conduct compliance training and audits.</p>\r\n<p>● Prepare compliance reports and documentation.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Key Qualifications:</strong></p>\r\n<p>● Bachelor&rsquo;s Degree in Law, Finance, Business, or related field.</p>\r\n<p>● 0&ndash;2 years of experience in compliance or regulatory affairs (fintech experience is an added advantage).</p>\r\n<p>● Strong understanding of African financial regulations.</p>\r\n<p>● Excellent organizational and communication skills.</p>\r\n<p>● High attention to detail and integrity.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Additional Information:</strong></p>\r\n<p>● Competitive salary and benefits.</p>\r\n<p>● Opportunity to advance your career in a reputable fintech company.</p>\r\n<p>● Women are encouraged to apply.</p>\r\n<p>If you are committed to upholding standards and ready to excel as a Compliance &amp; Regulatory Specialist, we&rsquo;d love to meet you!</p>', NULL, 'Competitive', 1, 'full-time', 'Nairobi, Kenya', 106, NULL, '2025-05-19 12:10:08', '2025-05-19 12:10:45', 'open', '2025-05-27', 1),
(19, 1, NULL, NULL, 'Cybersecurity Analyst', 'cybersecurity-analyst', '<p><strong>Job Overview: </strong></p>\r\n<p>We are seeking a vigilant and proactive Cybersecurity Analyst to safeguard our platforms and customer data. The ideal candidate will implement robust security measures and respond to emerging threats. This is a fantastic opportunity to work in a high-impact, rapidly evolving sector.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\r\n<p>● Monitor systems for security breaches and respond to incidents.</p>\r\n<p>● Implement and update cybersecurity protocols and policies.</p>\r\n<p>● Conduct regular vulnerability assessments and penetration tests.</p>\r\n<p>● Ensure compliance with regulatory standards.</p>\r\n<p>● Prepare security reports and educate staff on best practices.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Key Qualifications:</strong></p>\r\n<p>● Bachelor&rsquo;s Degree in Information Security, Computer Science, or related field.</p>\r\n<p>● 0&ndash;2 years of experience in cybersecurity (fintech experience is an added advantage).</p>\r\n<p>● Familiarity with security frameworks and regulatory compliance.</p>\r\n<p>● Proficiency in security tools and software.</p>\r\n<p>● Strong analytical and problem-solving skills.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Additional Information:</strong></p>\r\n<p>● Competitive salary and benefits package.</p>\r\n<p>● Opportunity to grow your career in a cutting-edge tech environment.</p>\r\n<p>● Women are encouraged to apply.</p>\r\n<p>If you are detail-oriented and ready to protect digital finance as a Cybersecurity Analyst, join our team!</p>', NULL, 'Competitive', 1, 'full-time', 'Nairobi, Kenya', 106, NULL, '2025-05-19 12:13:30', '2025-05-19 12:14:03', 'open', '2025-05-27', 1),
(20, 1, NULL, NULL, 'Sales Executive', 'sales-executive', '<p><strong>Job Summary:</strong><br>The VFS Sales Executive is responsible for driving the promotion and sales of VFS&rsquo;s value-added<br>services. This includes delivering customized VAS solutions to clients and actively seeking sales<br>opportunities. The role focuses on building strong relationships with travel agencies, managing both<br>online and offline promotional efforts, analysing market trends, and implementing strategic<br>marketing initiatives to achieve revenue targets.<br><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong><br>&bull; <strong><em>Sales &amp; Promotion of Value-Added Services</em></strong>:<br>- Actively promote and sell VFS&rsquo;s value-added services to both new and existing clients.<br>- Identify client needs and offer tailored VAS solutions that enhance their experience<br>while meeting company revenue goals.<br>- Stay updated on new and evolving value-added service offerings, ensuring effective<br>communication to customers.<br>&bull; <em><strong>Customer Relationship Management:</strong></em><br>-Build and maintain strong, long-lasting relationships with corporate clients, schools &amp;<br>universities, travel agencies, and individual customers to maximize sales<br>opportunities.<br>- Provide exceptional customer service and address client inquiries regarding VFS<br>value-added options.<br>- Collaborate closely with internal teams to ensure a seamless, positive customer<br>experience.<br>&bull; <em><strong>Sales Target Achievement</strong></em>:<br>- Set and exceed sales targets for value-added services, contributing to the overall<br>growth and profitability of the organization.<br>- Regularly track sales performance and provide reports to the management team.<br>- Conduct market analysis to identify new business opportunities and areas for<br>potential sales growth.<br><em><strong>&bull; Product Knowledge &amp; Training:</strong></em><br>- Maintain an in-depth understanding of all VFS products and services, including the<br>features, benefits, and pricing of value-added services.<br>- Provide product training to new and existing staff to ensure they are well-equipped to<br>effectively promote and sell services.<br><em><strong>&bull; Marketing &amp; Outreach:</strong></em><br>- Assist in the creation and execution of marketing campaigns to drive awareness and<br>sales of value-added services.<br>- Participate in outreach events, fairs, and webinars to generate leads and promote VFS<br>offerings.<br><em><strong>&bull; Reporting &amp; Documentation:</strong></em><br>- Prepare comprehensive sales reports and forecasts for management review.<br>- Document client interactions, sales progress, and customer feedback.<br><strong>Qualifications:</strong><br>&bull; Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Business Administration, Marketing, or a related field (preferred).<br>&bull; Proven experience in sales, customer service, or business development (experience in travel or<br>visa services is a plus).<br>&bull; Strong interpersonal and communication skills with the ability to engage and persuade<br>clients.<br>&bull; Ability to work independently, meet deadlines, and exceed sales targets.<br>&bull; Proficiency in Microsoft Office Suite and CRM software.<br><strong>Personal Attributes:</strong><br>&bull; Self-motivated, goal-oriented, and results-driven.<br>&bull; Strong problem-solving, negotiation, and decision-making skills.<br>&bull; Team player with the ability to collaborate across departments.<br>&bull; Customer-centric with a passion for sales and client satisfaction.<br><strong>Work Environment</strong>:<br>This role requires working in a fast-paced environment, interacting with both clients and internal<br>teams. Occasional travel may be required for client meetings or promotional activities.</p>', NULL, '95000', 1, 'full-time', 'Nairobi, Kenya', 106, NULL, '2025-05-21 09:48:52', '2025-05-21 09:49:20', 'open', '2025-05-30', 1),
