(23, 1, NULL, NULL, '2nd Cook/Food Handler', '2nd-cookfood-handler', '<p><strong>DESCRIPTION OF JOB TASK AND RESPONSIBILITIES:</strong><br> Performs full range of simple cooking tasks.<br> Weighs, measures and dispenses foods in accordance with portion controls<br> Mixes ingredients according to precisely written recipes.<br> Sets up and replenishes food/salad bar.<br> Cleans and maintains equipment and work areas.<br> Knowledge of the methods and procedures relating to food preparation in small quantities and the skill to apply such information to cook a limited variety of prepared foods.<br> Ability to read and understand written food service material such as food labels; standardizes recipes, etc. frequently lifts or move objects weighing up to 40lbs.<br> Ensures proper portion control for food, condiments and supplies are accurate<br> Expected to adhere to fire, safety and sanitation standards<br> Keeps work area clean and neat at all times. At the end of shift cleans and sanitizes work area<br> Maintains highest standards of sanitation<br> Maintains temperature controls, labeling and dating consumable items<br> Strictly adheres to FIFO method when pulling or using stocks<br> Assistant to cook<br> Performs other related duties as required</p>\r\n<p><strong>BASIC JOB QUALIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Must speak, read, and understand the English language.</li>\r\n<li>Must pass overseas medical screening and be in good health.</li>\r\n<li><span class=\"OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">All work-related training certificates</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">Valid Passport Copy</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">COVID-19 vaccination certificate</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">Employment certificate/ Recommendation letters</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><br><strong>JOB SPECIFICATIONS: SPECIAL CERTIFICATIONS OR TRAINING</strong><br> Food Handler Certificate.<br> Adult First Aid, CPR and AED Training Certificate<br> Star Service Training Certificate<br> ServSafe</p>\r\n<p><strong>EDUCATION:</strong><br> Diploma graduate or related fields</p>\r\n<p><br><strong>EXPERIENCE:</strong><br>1. Minimum of one (2) year of experience as 2nd Cook/Food Handler, Short Order Cook, and/or Cook. Must know how to follow recipes and combine ingredients for plain and other cooked dishes.</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Qualified and interested applicants who meet the specifications are requested to send their updated CVs to vacancies@amsol.africa by 6th June 2025.</li>\r\n<li>*Kindly indicate the position applied for in the subject line of the email</li>\r\n<li>Applications will be reviewed on a rolling basis, and only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', NULL, '$ 510', 1, 'full-time', 'Diego Garcia, UK', 106, NULL, '2025-05-22 09:47:17', '2025-05-22 09:47:54', 'open', '2025-06-25', 1);
