(54, 1, NULL, NULL, 'Theatre Team Leader', 'theatre-team-leader', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Role Summary</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt 21.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">To promote and maintain caring, highly professional standards of perioperative nursing <span style=\"background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">ensuring safe and quality care to patients</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt 21.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt 21.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">The team leader is expected to supervise staff in all aspects of managing the unit and the resources <span style=\"background: white; mso-highlight: white;\">while</span> promoting job satisfaction for the theatre team.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Duties and Responsibilities</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;</span></strong