sp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Perform daily rounds ensuring<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>a clean and safe environment is maintained for the patients at all times.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo10; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Maintain quarterly theatre contamination checks</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo10; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Ensure staff report early for planned surgeries and receive report at 7.30am everyday </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo10; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Maintain and allocate nursing teams considering competencies and skills, ensuring each individual staff delivers to expectations.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo10; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Be keen and pay attention to the doctors&rsquo; needs and preferences to ensure smooth surgical procedures.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo10; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Ensure the planned surgical procedures are carried out as scheduled and planned</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo10; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Creating of monthly rota, ensuring correct skills mix and considering that those who are learning are allocated to cover sessions</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo10; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">To always ensure handover between shifts<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>are completed and documented for all cadres of staff</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo10; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Maintain inventory of equipment and instruments, with quarterly major counts and reports</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo10; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Ensure and safeguard the hospital /patients and equipment from damage, wastage or loss.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo10; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Take responsibility for doing the following and for ensuring maintenance of accurate records/ documentation for:</span></p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin-top: 0in;\" start=\"1\" type=\"1\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l5 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Site marking</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l5 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Surgical Safety checklist</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l5 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Medication records chart</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l5 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Fluid charts</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l5 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Nursing Cardex</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l5 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Surgical Instrument and swab count sheet</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l5 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Nursing Care plans</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l5 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Family and patient education</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l5 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Discharge summary</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l5 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Charge sheet</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l5 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Specimen movement and records</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l5 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Monthly quality and process indicators</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo9; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Ensure monthly theatre reports- accurate statistics, quality control theatre utilization, theatre delays and any other reports as required</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo9; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Call more surgeons and anaesthetists to use the facility and maintain quality<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>services to ensure retention</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo9; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Have in place processes that reduce wastage in all areas</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow: 2;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 98.25pt; border: solid black 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 5.0pt 5.0pt 5.0pt 5.0pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"164\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">PEOPLE</span></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 371.25pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid black 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 5.0pt 5.0pt 5.0pt 5.0pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"619\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Internal ;-</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l10 level1 lfo5; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Communicate with other professional staff both in and out of the theatre to ensure that the care given to patients is of appropriate standard.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l10 level1 lfo5; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Make sure that all information concerning patients and their treatment remains confidential at all times.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l10 level1 lfo5; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Build capacity of teams by ensuring all staff are trained and skill checked<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>twice a year</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l10 level1 lfo5; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">perform random skill checks on staff regularly</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l10 level1 lfo5; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Ensure staff report on time</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l10 level1 lfo5; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Monthly departmental meetings</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l10 level1 lfo5; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Teach and delegate role of shift incharge</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l10 level1 lfo5; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">liaise with doctors to identify their challenges and encourage their use of the theatre</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l10 level1 lfo5; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Liaise with other HODs to ensure patients and doctors have a good experience</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow: 3; mso-yfti-lastrow: yes;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 98.25pt; border: solid black 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 5.0pt 5.0pt 5.0pt 5.0pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"164\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 371.25pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid black 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 5.0pt 5.0pt 5.0pt 5.0pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"619\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">External;-</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Maintain personal contact with the doctors to ensure their needs are met, and grievances addressed.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">●<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Be observant of the patients&rsquo; needs and requirements, and assist where appropriate in providing care to meet those needs which are within the total care plan of the patient.</spa