(55, 1, NULL, NULL, 'Pharmaceutical Technologist', 'pharmaceutical-technologist', '<p><strong>The Role</strong></p>\r\n<p>As a Pharmaceutical Technologist, you will play a key role in the efficient operation of our clinic-based pharmacies. This position offers an exciting opportunity to be part of a growing healthcare service that prioritizes patient care and operational excellence.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\r\n<p>&middot; Medication Dispensing:</p>\r\n<p>o Accurately dispense prescription medications in accordance with physician orders and regulatory guidelines.</p>\r\n<p>o Provide clear and concise instructions to patients on medication usage.</p>\r\n<p>&middot; Inventory Management:</p>\r\n<p>o Maintain proper inventory levels and reorder medications and supplies as needed.</p>\r\n<p>o Accurately record all transactions in the Ilara Health HMIS</p>\r\n<p>o Conduct regular audits to ensure accurate stock levels and expiration date monitoring.</p>\r\n<p>&middot; Collaboration and Communication:</p>\r\n<p>o Work closely with other professionals at Ilara Health and at the clinic to ensure coordinated patient care.</p>\r\n<p>o Communicate effectively with Ilara Health team members and hospital staff.</p>\r\n<p>&middot; Regulatory Compliance:</p>\r\n<p>o Ensure compliance with local regulations governing pharmacy practices.</p>\r\n<p>o Participate in quality assurance and continuous improvement initiatives.</p>\r\n<p>&middot; Customer Service:</p>\r\n<p>o Provide excellent customer service to patients, addressing their inquiries and concerns.</p>\r\n<p>o Maintain a professional and approachable demeanor at all times.</p>\r\n<p>&middot; Cleaning and Maintenance:</p>\r\n<p>o Perform regular cleaning tasks to ensure a sanitary and organized pharmacy environment.</p>\r\n<p>o Adhere to infection prevention and control standards and protocols to maintain a clean and safe workspace.</p>\r\n<p>&middot; Billing:</p>\r\n<p>o Accurately process patient billing, ensuring compliance with billing regulations and hospital policies.</p>\r\n<p>o Address billing inquiries from patients and collaborate with the billing department as needed.</p>\r\n<p>o Collection of revenue and adhering to cash handling policies.</p>\r\n<p>&middot; Day-to-Day Tasks:</p>\r\n<p>o Handle various day-to-day tasks to contribute to the smooth operation of the pharmacy.</p>\r\n<p>o Assist in administrative duties and maintain accurate records as required.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\r\n<p>&middot; Licensed Pharmaceutical Technologist.</p>\r\n<p>&middot; Minimum of 2 years of experience working in a hospital or clinical pharmacy setting.</p>\r\n<p>&middot; Strong knowledge of pharmaceutical regulations and best practices.</p>\r\n<p>&middot; Excellent attention to detail and organizational skills.</p>\r\n<p>&middot; Effective communication and interpersonal abilities.</p>\r\n<p>&middot; Tech-savviness: Comfortably navigate inventory softwares, EMR systems, and other digital tools to deliver seamless dispensing experiences.</p>', NULL, 'Competitive', 1, 'full-time', 'Nairobi, Kenya', 106, NULL, '2025-07-17 10:03:25', '2025-07-17 10:03:57', 'open', '2025-07-31', 1),
(56, 1, NULL, NULL, 'Digital Sales Executive', 'digital-sales-executive', '<h3 data-start=\"286\" data-end=\"308\"><strong data-start=\"290\" data-end=\"306\">Job Summary:</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-start=\"309\" data-end=\"727\">We are seeking a highly motivated and results-driven <strong data-start=\"362\" data-end=\"399\">Digital Sales Executive</strong> to join our growing team. The ideal candidate should have a strong understanding of digital marketing products and tools, excellent analytical skills, and a proven ability to generate and close sales. You should be data-driven, skilled in Google Ads, and well-versed in the use of social media platforms for business marketing.</p>\r\n<hr data-start=\"729\" data-end=\"732\">\r\n<h3 data-start=\"734\" data-end=\"763\"><strong data-start=\"738\" data-end=\"763\">Key Responsibilities:</strong></h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"764\" data-end=\"1514\">\r\n<li data-start=\"764\" data-end=\"852\">\r\n<p data-start=\"766\" data-end=\"852\">Actively prospect, pitch, and close sales for digital marketing products and services.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"853\" data-end=\"1009\">\r\n<p data-start=\"855\" data-end=\"1009\">Identify client needs and propose suitable digital marketing solutions, including SEO, PPC (Google Ads), social media marketing, email marketing, and more.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1010\" data-end=\"1093\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1012\" data-end=\"1093\">Work closely with the marketing team to understand product offerings and updates.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1094\" data-end=\"1201\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1096\" data-end=\"1201\">Analyze sales data and digital campaign performance to improve conversion rates and customer acquisition.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1202\" data-end=\"1293\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1204\" data-end=\"1293\">Develop and maintain strong client relationships to ensure repeat business and referrals.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1294\" data-end=\"1363\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1296\" data-end=\"1363\">Prepare and deliver sales presentations tailored to clients\' needs.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1364\" data-end=\"1459\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1366\" data-end=\"1459\">Keep abreast of market trends, competitor offerings, and best practices in digital marketing.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1460\" data-end=\"1514\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1462\" data-end=\"1514\">Meet and exceed monthly and quarterly sales targets.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr data-start=\"1516\" data-end=\"1519\">\r\n<h3 data-start=\"1521\" data-end=\"1553\"><strong data-start=\"1525\" data-end=\"1553\">Qualifications &amp; Skills:</strong></h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1554\" data-end=\"2221\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1554\" data-end=\"1632\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1556\" data-end=\"1632\">Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Marketing, Business, Communication, or a related field.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1633\" data-end=\"1710\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1635\" data-end=\"1710\">Minimum of 2 years&rsquo; experience in digital marketing, sales or related field.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1711\" data-end=\"1825\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1713\" data-end=\"1825\">Strong knowledge of digital marketing products, including Google Ads, SEO, Facebook Ads, and other PPC platforms.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1826\" data-end=\"1916\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1828\" data-end=\"1916\">Familiarity with analytics and data tools (e.g., Google Analytics, Meta Business Suite).</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1917\" data-end=\"1967\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1919\" data-end=\"1967\">Excellent communication and presentation skills.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1968\" data-end=\"2086\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1970\" data-end=\"2086\">Proficiency in using social media platforms (Facebook, Instagram, LinkedIn, Twitter, TikTok) for marketing purposes.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"2087\" data-end=\"2147\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2089\" data-end=\"2147\">Goal-oriented with a passion for sales and digital trends.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"2148\" data-end=\"2221\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2150\" data-end=\"2221\">Self-driven with strong problem-solving and analytical thinking skills.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr data-start=\"2223\" data-end=\"2226\">\r\n<h3 data-start=\"2228\" data-end=\"2250\"><strong data-start=\"2232\" data-end=\"2250\">What We Offer:</strong></h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"2251\" data-end=\"2428\">\r\n<li data-start=\"2251\" data-end=\"2288\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2253\" data-end=\"2288\">Competitive salary plus commission.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"2289\" data-end=\"2320\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2291\" data-end=\"2320\">Performance-based incentives.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"2321\" data-end=\"2370\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2323\" data-end=\"2370\">Professional growth and learning opportunities.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"2371\" data-end=\"2428\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2373\" data-end=\"2428\">A dynamic, tech-savvy, and supportive team environment.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Competitive', 2, 'full-time', 'Nairobi, Kenya', 94, NULL, '2025-08-05 11:41:03', '2025-08-05 11:49:29', 'open', NULL, 1),
(57, 1, NULL, NULL, 'PHP/WordPress Developer', 'phpwordpress-developer', '<h3 data-start=\"355\" data-end=\"377\"><strong data-start=\"359\" data-end=\"375\">Job Summary:</strong></h3>\r\n<p data-start=\"378\" data-end=\"689\">We are looking for a passionate and self-driven Entry-Level Developer with hands-on knowledge in <strong data-start=\"475\" data-end=\"482\">PHP</strong>, <strong data-start=\"484\" data-end=\"495\">Laravel</strong>, and <strong data-start=\"501\" data-end=\"514\">WordPress</strong>. The ideal candidate should have a basic understanding of backend development, CMS customization, and a willingness to learn and grow in a fast-paced development environment.</p>\r\n<hr data-start=\"691\" data-end=\"694\">\r\n<h3 data-start=\"696\" data-end=\"725\"><strong data-start=\"700\" data-end=\"725\">Key Responsibilities:</strong></h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"726\" data-end=\"1237\">\r\n<li data-start=\"726\" data-end=\"821\">\r\n<p data-start=\"728\" data-end=\"821\">Assist in the design, development, and maintenance of web applications using PHP and Laravel.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"822\" data-end=\"885\">\r\n<p data-start=\"824\" data-end=\"885\">Customize, update, and manage WordPress websites and plugins.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"886\" data-end=\"978\">\r\n<p data-start=\"888\" data-end=\"978\">Collaborate with senior developers, designers, and other team members on ongoing projects.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"979\" data-end=\"1059\">\r\n<p data-start=\"981\" data-end=\"1059\">Debug and troubleshoot technical issues in existing applications and websites.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1060\" data-end=\"1128\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1062\" data-end=\"1128\">Participate in code reviews and follow best development practices.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1129\" data-end=\"1179\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1131\" data-end=\"1179\">Write clean, scalable, and well-documented code.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1180\" data-end=\"1237\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1182\" data-end=\"1237\">Stay updated with emerging web technologies and trends.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr data-start=\"1239\" data-end=\"1242\">\r\n<h3 data-start=\"1244\" data-end=\"1265\"><strong data-start=\"1248\" data-end=\"1265\">Requirements:</strong></h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1266\" data-end=\"1675\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1266\" data-end=\"1327\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1268\" data-end=\"1327\">Basic knowledge of <strong data-start=\"1287\" data-end=\"1294\">PHP</strong>, <strong data-start=\"1296\" data-end=\"1307\">Laravel</strong>, and <strong data-start=\"1313\" data-end=\"1326\">WordPress</strong>.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1328\" data-end=\"1396\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1330\" data-end=\"1396\">Understanding of <strong data-start=\"1347\" data-end=\"1355\">HTML</strong>, <strong data-start=\"1357\" data-end=\"1364\">CSS</strong>, <strong data-start=\"1366\" data-end=\"1380\">JavaScript</strong>, and <strong data-start=\"1386\" data-end=\"1395\">MySQL</strong>.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1397\" data-end=\"1461\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1399\" data-end=\"1461\">Familiarity with version control tools like <strong data-start=\"1443\" data-end=\"1450\">Git</strong> is a plus.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1462\" data-end=\"1510\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1464\" data-end=\"1510\">Good problem-solving and communication skills.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1511\" data-end=\"1577\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1513\" data-end=\"1577\">Eagerness to learn and adapt to new technologies and frameworks.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1578\" data-end=\"1675\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1580\" data-end=\"1675\">Diploma or Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Computer Science, IT, or a related field is an added advantage.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr data-start=\"1677\" data-end=\"1680\">\r\n<h3 data-start=\"1682\" data-end=\"1703\"><strong data-start=\"1686\" data-end=\"1703\">Nice to Have:</strong></h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1704\" data-end=\"1863\">\r\n<li data-start=\"170